name: Choose 10 Stevie Ray Vaughan 1986 Concert Photos
description:
Stevie Ray Vaughan & Rare Fender Stratocaster
Choose 10 original 8" X 10" Black & White photographs

I took these pictures in St. Paul, Minnesota, July 11th, 1986 at the RiverFest Concert. The white guitar is a rare 1980 Fender "Jimi Hendrix Model" Stratocaster; the same construction as the 25TH ANNIVERSARY, except that it had a reverse headstock and an additional body contour on the front. According to Fender only 25 of this highly unusual Strats were ever made. Stevie purchased this guitar that very day at PETE'S GUITAR in St. Paul, Mn.
